{"tid":392350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近200萬內地新移民未來50年湧港　　　 溝淡港人","createTime":"2017-09-08T12:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T08:21:54.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bf8ef94857fae9cd15367421e34fba70b69f3c","tid":392350,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"統計處指，本港去年勞動人口有362萬，但隨人口老化會逐漸下降。勞動人口會由2019年至2022年之間約367至368萬高位，下降至2066年只313萬，勞動人口參與率也跌至49.6%。政府發言人則表示，內地當局沒計劃更改每日150個單程證名額。<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處在未來50年的人口推算指出，香港人口將持續有淨流入，而單程證持有人是淨遷移的主要組成部份。處方考慮到單程證持有人近年來港趨勢，故採用每日100名或每年3.65萬單程證持有人來港作長遠假設。統計處推算，未來50年本港有189萬單程證持有人來港，平均每年3.78萬人。若每日用盡150個單程證配額，未來50年持單程證來港達273.75萬人，平均每年5.475萬人。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟成員譚凱邦指出，未來50年有189萬單程證人士來港，這數字可用恐怖來形容，香港對單程證無審批權，即來港人士的年齡、性別及財政狀況均不由香港控制，所以根本無法確保新移民人口可減輕本港人口老化或增加勞動力，但卻肯定加重本港房屋、醫療及福利的負荷。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，未來香港人口增長單一來源是內地，亦令人擔心香港會被「溝淡」，新移民帶來的內地文化會取代香港一直珍重的自由、民主、法治等核心價值。譚凱邦表示，香港有需要取回單程證審批權，並將每天單程證配額150個減半，平衡家庭團聚的需求與本港的負載能力。"},{"pid":"f51211e83b58069d16cdf7a411d7b64be2d60a05","tid":392350,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"2066年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知乜野朝代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404616f022e2e863f614bee06ff88e0b3951f352","tid":392350,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"遲d香港仲有無廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8dad5ff65fe806ed51702a834ea815ebc7c0bf2","tid":392350,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲d香港仲有無廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時香港人就好似宜家新界原居民咁樣，邊境都拆走咗好耐"},{"pid":"13cba298b519c7a1dbe5c55abcef36bff7c7007a","tid":392350,"uid":6195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都未計落到嚟再生個堆蝗卵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加多倍就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed90e387eebf6d592b0cc2736278df0415de724c","tid":392350,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲d香港仲有無廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我近排買嘢啲店員都同我講支那話，一次屈臣氏，一次Zara，屌香港仲係咪人住"},{"pid":"caa6b5b1bc455a7e00883bbe9c295ce6acd33107","tid":392350,"uid":53278,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"上面咁撚好境 撈得掂既點會落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落得黎既 一係七老八十 一係字都唔識多隻"},{"pid":"9ca136158d20dac64808f52359d1d925b6c874ef","tid":392350,"uid":38884,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面咁撚好境 撈得掂既點會落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落得黎既 一係七老八十 一係字都唔識多隻</blockquote><br />\n大把上高有樓 再落黎呃飯食"},{"pid":"d8c0cb863e51e3808dbf59c1c484b650a8956e8a","tid":392350,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"準備被溝淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8214062b23c7c1fd73798ec707f752a002d812c1","tid":392350,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"儲定錢移民算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm